{"tid":331340,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"癲狗系列 - 炒龍躉球","createTime":"2017-07-22T05:53:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-24T09:01:15.000Z","uid":74981,"like":19,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"63718ef440c3a0ed1176f4d366b2b2439a9a89bc","tid":331340,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T05:53:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s4.postimg.org/khzzt1t7h/FISH_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs4.postimg.org%2Fkhzzt1t7h%2FFISH_1.jpg&h=de34361b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>影片如下:</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/k1D3WihPSdU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fk1D3WihPSdU&d=2Yu%2B9NqC7gQ3dQGc9WbouMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=0ca51f1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/k1D3WihPSdU</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>材料:</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n龍躉腩位10兩切厚片<br />\n<br />\n薑片數片<br />\n<br />\n乾蔥頭2粒切片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>醃料:</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n鹽1/2茶匙<br />\n<br />\n胡椒粉少許 (有冇都得)<br />\n<br />\n豆粉水少許<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>調味:</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n酒2-3茶匙<br />\n<br />\n雞湯4茶匙<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>芡汁:</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n水1湯匙<br />\n<br />\n豆粉1/3茶匙<br />\n<br />\n胡椒粉少許<br />\n<br />\n鹽1/3茶匙<br />\n<br />\n麻油 (有冇都得)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>做法慨述:</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n1. 醃龍躉肉5-10分鐘<br />\n<br />\n2. 燒紅獲, 落油, 油溫5成, 熄火落龍躉肉, 唔好係咁郁佢.<br />\n<br />\n3. 炸一陣, 反一反佢, 開番少少火炸一陣, 5成熟隔油撈起<br />\n<br />\n4. 洗獲, 燒紅獲, 落多D油朗獲, 倒剩少少油, 爆香薑片和乾蔥頭<br />\n<br />\n5. 贊酒, 落龍躉肉, 再落雞湯, 用慢火, 唔好郁D龍躉<br />\n<br />\n6. 埋芡炒, 再番開大火炒至收汁, 完成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a30945fe42c2f1eb3a519523e46698dfd1bf03c","tid":331340,"uid":64318,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T05:55:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17fafaaf97c4213dbb3c9214b0b575175e8af5a5","tid":331340,"uid":45182,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T05:55:38.000Z","msg":"睇落又好似幾好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6823c0ebae33afc353c9de3d1fca25b54ef606c6","tid":331340,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T05:56:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44bd7397ae8c941c26656f4f50602adb6135ac96","tid":331340,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T05:56:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f4d087e250f1a0259122b879a95ca7926750e7d","tid":331340,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T05:56:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇落又好似幾好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4b3e3f11d41655d004e9f122de3fe704eaf5114","tid":331340,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T05:56:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雞扒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5e6ad9e6a54dc0691dde1a21a2dd3d90d853034","tid":331340,"uid":71826,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T05:57:55.000Z","msg":"肥絲仲未入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34aff49ae6d27a51c01975bd9d9f476f4e4c4562","tid":331340,"uid":45431,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T05:58:10.000Z","msg":"下次加返西芹/西蘭花，擺碟靚啲又有兩條菜咬下健康啲"},{"pid":